Class NetBeansChatConfig

java.lang.Object
uno.anahata.ai.config.ChatConfig
uno.anahata.ai.swing.SwingChatConfig
uno.anahata.ai.nb.NetBeansChatConfig
public class NetBeansChatConfig extends SwingChatConfig
NetBeans-specific implementation of SwingChatConfig. It manages the registration of IDE-specific tools and context providers.
